</a>
<h2 class="bold font-l">Brain Dead 13</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
Dr Neurosis' gardens have lots of green acid that has the same consistency as water and will melt Lance to the bone in an instant should he fall in. </p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="alt-titles section section-fact">
<h3>
<strong>Alternative Title(s):</strong>
<span>Hydrogen Hollywoodide</span>, <span>Super Acid</span>, <span>Super Corrosive Acid</span>, <span>Hyper Corrosive Acid</span> </h3>
</div>
